                                                                        </b></p>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="row justify-content-between">
                                                                <div class="col">
                                                                    <p class="mb-1"><b>Shipping</b></p>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="flex-sm-col col-auto">
                                                                    <p class="mb-1"><b>0 SEK</b></p>
